<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٩٥:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم: طه <span class="c2">(١)</span>} <span class="c4">[طه: ١]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ،<span class="c5"> وَالضَّحَّاكُ:</span> بِالنَّبَطِيَّةِ: <span class="c2">(أَيْ طَهْ)</span>: يَا رَجُلُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>